- cs.CR (Cryptography and Security) is a possible category as the paper mentions working with traffic that is encrypted via TLS. 
- cs.SI (Social and Information Networks) is a possible category as the paper deals with analyzing IP flows in real time. 
- cs.IT (Information Theory) is a less likely category but still possible as the paper deals with estimating parameters of an application-layer protocol.
